title: Angular.dev - Building dynamic forms documentation page has link to non-existent image
body:
### Describe the problem that you experienced

When you go to the 'Building dynamic forms' documentation page, it references at the very bottom an image. I've looked in the codebase and the example under the same filename exists for `aio` but not `adev`.

Could this please be included as I'd like to see the final outcome :smile:

Page link - https://angular.dev/guide/forms/dynamic-forms
